PRODUCT REQUIREMENTS BRIEF

PROBLEM: {problem}

TARGET AUDIENCE: {audience}

SUCCESS METRIC: {success_metric}

CONSTRAINTS: {constraints}

Directions for AI: Generate a full PRD including:
1. Problem statement (1 paragraph)
2. User stories with acceptance criteria
3. Edge cases (minimum 5)
4. Technical considerations
5. Success metrics and measurement approach
6. Risks and mitigations

Be thorough. Cover what users will see AND what happens when things go wrong.
